title: [Miasmal Forest, Ghostly Trees]
description: Rotting reeds and marsh grasses mix with the turbid water to befoul the air with a noxious stench.  The sickly trees rising from the miasma look like skeletal figures reaching into the befouled mist.  The trails disappear into the thick chalky mist.
